---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Education">
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-3">Education</h1>
      <p class="text-center text-muted-foreground mb-12">Degrees and certifications</p>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-10">
        <section aria-labelledby="formal-education">
          <h2 id="formal-education" class="text-xl font-semibold text-headings mb-4">Formal education</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-6">
            <li class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
              <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 mb-2">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-white border border-border p-1 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden shrink-0">
                    <img src="/logos/bits-pilani.svg" alt="BITS Pilani logo" class="w-full h-full object-contain" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.parentElement.nextElementSibling?.classList.remove('sr-only')" />
                  </div>
                  <span data-fallback class="sr-only w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-muted text-muted-foreground text-xs font-semibold flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">BITS</span>
                  <div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">MSc. Data Science & AI</h3>
                    <p class="text-primary font-medium">BITS Pilani Digital</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-sm text-muted-foreground shrink-0">Sep 2025 – Present</div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">Currently pursuing a master's program focused on data science and artificial intelligence.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
              <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 mb-2">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-white border border-border p-1 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden shrink-0">
                    <img src="/logos/makaut.svg" alt="MAKAUT logo" class="w-full h-full object-contain" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.parentElement.nextElementSibling?.classList.remove('sr-only')" />
                  </div>
                  <span data-fallback class="sr-only w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-muted text-muted-foreground text-xs font-semibold flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">MAKAUT</span>
                  <div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">BSc. Data Science</h3>
                    <p class="text-primary font-medium">Maulana Abul Kalam Azad University of Technology, West Bengal</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-sm text-muted-foreground shrink-0">Sep 2022 – Jul 2025</div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4">CGPA: <span class="font-medium text-foreground">8.3</span></div>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">Completed a 3-year BSc in Data Science with a strong foundation in statistics, machine learning, data analysis, and visualization.</p>
            </li>

            <li class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
              <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 mb-2">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-white border border-border p-1 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden shrink-0">
                    <img src="/logos/wbchse.png" alt="WBCHSE logo" class="w-full h-full object-contain" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.parentElement.nextElementSibling?.classList.remove('sr-only')" />
                  </div>
                  <span data-fallback class="sr-only w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-muted text-muted-foreground text-xs font-semibold flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">WBCHSE</span>
                  <div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Higher Secondary (Science)</h3>
                    <p class="text-primary font-medium">Gournagar High School — WBCHSE</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-sm text-muted-foreground shrink-0">Jul 2022</div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4">Percentage: <span class="font-medium text-foreground">64.40%</span></div>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">Focused on Mathematics, Physics, Chemistry, Computer Science, Bengali, and English.</p>
            </li>

            <li class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
              <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 mb-2">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-white border border-border p-1 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden shrink-0">
                    <img src="/logos/wbbse.png" alt="WBBSE logo" class="w-full h-full object-contain" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.parentElement.nextElementSibling?.classList.remove('sr-only')" />
                  </div>
                  <span data-fallback class="sr-only w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-muted text-muted-foreground text-xs font-semibold flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">WBBSE</span>
                  <div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Secondary</h3>
                    <p class="text-primary font-medium">Gournagar High School — WBBSE</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-sm text-muted-foreground shrink-0">Jul 2020</div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4">Percentage: <span class="font-medium text-foreground">78.86%</span></div>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">Built a strong foundation across languages and quantitative subjects.</p>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section aria-labelledby="certifications">
          <h2 id="certifications" class="text-xl font-semibold text-headings mb-4">Certifications</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-3 list-disc pl-5 text-muted-foreground">
            <li>Python Programming Fundamentals — Microsoft — <a href="https://www.coursera.org/account/accomplishments/verify/14NUFGSP66LP" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-primary underline">Verify</a></li>
            <li>Data Analysis and Visualization with Python — Microsoft — <a href="https://www.coursera.org/account/accomplishments/verify/PVOY0YGZPDUD" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-primary underline">Verify</a></li>
            <li>Automation and Scripting with Python — Microsoft — <a href="https://www.coursera.org/account/accomplishments/verify/8CQF4VOLD7KS" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-primary underline">Verify</a></li>
            <li>Introduction to Data Analytics — Meta — <a href="https://www.coursera.org/account/accomplishments/verify/4BWBS67J5FZW" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-primary underline">Verify</a></li>
            <li>Data Analytics Course with Generative AI — Simplilearn — <a href="https://www.coursera.org/account/accomplishments/verify/MDKXMSCBVO35" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-primary underline">Verify</a></li>
          </ul>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>